    Interface Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Animation
    Allows for multiple objects to be treated as a unit and apply changes over time to each of its constiuent members.
    ColorfulObject
    A basic form of objects that adds color functionality
    PollyObject
    The most basic form of all objects that get added to slides (Back and White)
    SerialManager
    Facilitate serialization of objects for saving/opening/cloning purposes.
    Shape
    A type of ColorfulObject that allows for the utilization of Shapes from the processing library.
    TextObject
    A type of colorful object that strictly deals with text/strings.
    Window
    Acts as a conduit between the backend functionality and everything external to the backend package.
